  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/c95bb9681cd4a5afcbc61a0192fbff5b.webp?t=1715675195\" width=620 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/1369ca99c455c50b5ea06eb41cee40ae.poster.avif?t=1715675195\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/1369ca99c455c50b5ea06eb41cee40ae.webm?t=1715675195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Connect with friends and keep an eye on their progress, or select your rivals and show them who's boss. The fun is in the friendly competition!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/9e366a40e10c7ed60ba3d1e2f6439fb0.webp?t=1715675195\" width=620 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/f37cdfe212de8038eda453d8dc902656.poster.avif?t=1715675195\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/f37cdfe212de8038eda453d8dc902656.webm?t=1715675195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/f37cdfe212de8038eda453d8dc902656.mp4?t=1715675195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Push and Play: </strong>Now you can gently push other players aside to get ahead. It's a fun way to say \"excuse me\" while racing to the finish line!<br><br></li><li><strong>Cool Moves:</strong> Say hello with fun animations, music, and cool effects with our new Emotes wheel. It's like your character's own dance move!<br><br></li><li><strong>Chat While You Run:</strong> Talk to other players while you play with our simple text chat. Make plans or just joke around—it's all part of the game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/f601fe541bc7dff800bb0a2c3ac9f5f1.webp?t=1715675195\" width=620 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/1369ca99c455c50b5ea06eb41cee40ae.poster.avif?t=1715675195\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/1369ca99c455c50b5ea06eb41cee40ae.webm?t=1715675195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>For those who love the rush, our courses are designed for speedrunning. Find the quickest route, outpace your opponents, and set new records.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/c95bb9681cd4a5afcbc61a0192fbff5b.webp?t=1715675195\" width=620 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/1369ca99c455c50b5ea06eb41cee40ae.poster.avif?t=1715675195\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/1369ca99c455c50b5ea06eb41cee40ae.webm?t=1715675195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Connect with friends and keep an eye on their progress, or select your rivals and show them who's boss. The fun is in the friendly competition!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/9e366a40e10c7ed60ba3d1e2f6439fb0.webp?t=1715675195\" width=620 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/f37cdfe212de8038eda453d8dc902656.poster.avif?t=1715675195\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/f37cdfe212de8038eda453d8dc902656.webm?t=1715675195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/f37cdfe212de8038eda453d8dc902656.mp4?t=1715675195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Push and Play: </strong>Now you can gently push other players aside to get ahead. It's a fun way to say \"excuse me\" while racing to the finish line!<br><br></li><li><strong>Cool Moves:</strong> Say hello with fun animations, music, and cool effects with our new Emotes wheel. It's like your character's own dance move!<br><br></li><li><strong>Chat While You Run:</strong> Talk to other players while you play with our simple text chat. Make plans or just joke around—it's all part of the game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/f601fe541bc7dff800bb0a2c3ac9f5f1.webp?t=1715675195\" width=620 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/1369ca99c455c50b5ea06eb41cee40ae.poster.avif?t=1715675195\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497520/extras/1369ca99c455c50b5ea06eb41cee40ae.webm?t=1715675195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>For those who love the rush, our courses are designed for speedrunning. Find the quickest route, outpace your opponents, and set new records.</li></ul>",
